      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Super Shady Look-alike",
        "Client": "Carefree Hedgehog",
        "Description": "I thought that dumb faker was\r\nfollowing me around again, but\r\nturns out it was something else.\r\nI\u0027m getting real bad vibes from it.\r\nSend it packing and I\u0027ll hook you\r\nup with some materials to make\r\nsome sweet layered armor!",
